id=seiran_sysctl_guard
name=Seiran Sysctl Guard
version=v0.0.1
versionCode=20260703
author=superuseryu
description=Companion enforcement module for Seiran Kernel. Re-applies sysctl defaults post-boot that some ROM init.rc or vendor perf-hal configs silently override. WebUI included for TCP congestion control and CPU governor selection.
